## TMF API Reference : TMF 646 - Appointment An Appointment
is an arrangement to do something or meet someone at a
particular time and place. It is previously made during an
interaction or may be necessary to solve a customer problem
or to deliver a product order item. The appointment API goal
is to manage an appointment with all the necessary
characteristics. First, the API consists in searching free
time slots based on given parameters.
